## 2ï¸âƒ£ Common & Identical Shortcuts (No Adjustment Needed)

| Action | Excel | LibreOffice Calc | Status |
|-----|------|------------------|-------|
| Copy | Ctrl + C | Ctrl + C | âœ… Same |
| Paste | Ctrl + V | Ctrl + V | âœ… Same |
| Cut | Ctrl + X | Ctrl + X | âœ… Same |
| Save | Ctrl + S | Ctrl + S | âœ… Same |
| Undo | Ctrl + Z | Ctrl + Z | âœ… Same |
| Redo | Ctrl + Y | Ctrl + Y | âœ… Same |
| Select All | Ctrl + A | Ctrl + A | âœ… Same |
| Find | Ctrl + F | Ctrl + F | âœ… Same |
| Replace | Ctrl + H | Ctrl + H | âœ… Same |
| Print | Ctrl + P | Ctrl + P | âœ… Same |

