## 3ï¸âƒ£ Cell Navigation & Selection

| Action | Excel | LibreOffice Calc | Notes |
|-----|------|------------------|------|
| Edit cell | F2 | F2 | Identical |
| Move to data edge | Ctrl + Arrow | Ctrl + Arrow | Identical |
| Select to data edge | Ctrl + Shift + Arrow | Ctrl + Shift + Arrow | Identical |
| Move to first cell | Ctrl + Home | Ctrl + Home | Identical |
| Move to last cell | Ctrl + End | Ctrl + End | Slight behavior difference |

---

## 4ï¸âƒ£ Data Entry & Formatting

| Action | Excel | LibreOffice Calc | Status |
|-----|------|------------------|-------|
| Bold | Ctrl + B | Ctrl + B | Same |
| Italic | Ctrl + I | Ctrl + I | Same |
| Underline | Ctrl + U | Ctrl + U | Same |
| Format Cells | Ctrl + 1 | Ctrl + 1 | Same |
| Line break in cell | Alt + Enter | Alt + Enter | Same |

