## 5ï¸âƒ£ Excel Shortcuts That Differ or Are Missing

| Excel Shortcut | Purpose | LibreOffice Calc | Notes |
|---------------|--------|------------------|------|
| Ctrl + ; | Insert date | Different | Manual mapping recommended |
| Ctrl + Shift + ; | Insert time | Different | Manual mapping recommended |
| Alt + H | Ribbon Home | âŒ Not supported | Ribbon-only |
| Alt + A | Ribbon Data | âŒ Not supported | Ribbon-only |
| Alt + = | AutoSum | Partial | Toolbar/menu required |

